dataset.title: A new species of Parachute Gecko of the subgenus Ptychozoon (Sauria: Gekkonidae: Gekko) from the Indo-Burma region

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Lalremsanga, Hmar Tlawmte, Muansanga, Lal, Vabeiryureilai, Mathipi, Mirza, Zeeshan A. (2023): A new species of Parachute Gecko of the subgenus Ptychozoon (Sauria: Gekkonidae: Gekko) from the Indo-Burma region. Salamandra 59 (2): 1-11, DOI: http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7967275
